---
title: "US53 — Admin log in"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>LoginScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile
  A->>B: enter credentials
  B->>C: signIn()
  C->>E: verify credentials, load Profile
  E-->>C: session + role = admin
  C-->>B: signed in
  B-->>A: route to Admin portal (5-tab shell)
  note over E: credential check by Supabase Auth via AuthGateway
